{"tid":428591,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"快活谷啤酒節揭幕圖輯","createTime":"2017-10-08T07:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T07:45:05.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8c7b863cb04c043af3dfc58bdc2f6833986ca288","tid":428591,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:45:05.000Z","msg":"「快活谷啤酒節」今日揭幕，場內備有地道的德國啤酒、美食及娛樂，更有刺激的挑戰遊戲，讓馬迷吃喝暢玩，盡情盡勝。<br />\n<img src=\"http://prd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com/racingnews/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/10/rn20171005-p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fracingnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2017%2F10%2Frn20171005-p01.jpg&h=08a779dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://prd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com/racingnews/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/10/rn20171005-p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fracingnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2017%2F10%2Frn20171005-p02.jpg&h=86287e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國駐港副總領事Karsten Tietz（右）與香港賽馬會行政總裁應家柏（左）一同斟滿首杯啤酒，宣告節慶開始。<br />\n<img src=\"http://prd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com/racingnews/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/10/rn20171005-p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fracingnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2017%2F10%2Frn20171005-p03.jpg&h=4a827ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國駐港副總領事Karsten Tietz（右二）、馬會行政總裁應家柏（左二）、馬會賽馬業務及營運執行總監祁立賢(左一）、馬會賽事規管及發展執行總監夏定安（右一），與現場人士一起舉杯慶祝，場面熱鬧。<br />\n<img src=\"http://prd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com/racingnews/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/10/rn20171005-p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fracingnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2017%2F10%2Frn20171005-p04.jpg&h=404777b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://prd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com/racingnews/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/10/rn20171005-p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fracingnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2017%2F10%2Frn20171005-p05.jpg&h=8ced7726&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://prd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com/racingnews/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/10/rn20171005-p06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fracingnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2017%2F10%2Frn20171005-p06.jpg&h=026270c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://prd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com/racingnews/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/10/rn20171005-p07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fracingnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2017%2F10%2Frn20171005-p07.jpg&h=cec8705b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://prd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com/racingnews/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/10/rn20171005-p08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprd-hkjcwps3.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fracingnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2017%2F10%2Frn20171005-p08.jpg&h=17e862f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n場內特備口味眾多的正宗德國啤酒及美食，以及多項Oktoberfest啤酒節的挑戰遊戲，供馬迷吃喝暢玩。<br />\n<br />\n「快活谷啤酒節」將於10月11日、18日及25日繼續舉行。<br />\n<a href=\"http://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2017/10/05/%E5%BF%AB%E6%B4%BB%E8%B0%B7%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92%E7%AF%80%E6%8F%AD%E5%B9%95%E5%9C%96%E8%BC%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fracingnews.hkjc.com%2Fchinese%2F2017%2F10%2F05%2F%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E5%2595%25A4%25E9%2585%2592%25E7%25AF%2580%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%259C%2596%25E8%25BC%25AF%2F&d=QmfjLShgqAiVY21BAA36m4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=03d3eb68\" target=\"_blank\">http://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2017/10/05/%E5%BF%AB%E6%B4%BB%E8%B0%B7%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92%E7%AF%80%E6%8F%AD%E5%B9%95%E5%9C%96%E8%BC%AF/</a>"}]}